description: Kelly is in her new studio at Actionpark Media to discuss her kids sucking at soccer, drinking in high school, how she feels about fans taking photos and more. She's then joined by fellow Rams wives, Melissa Whitworth and Anna Kupp, to disucss their game day experience in Seattle, Kelly having a mortifying moment on the plane ride up, how they all met their husbands and much more!The Morning After podcast is produced by ACTIONPARK MEDIA. Follow us on Social Media:@actionparkmediagroup @kbstafford89@themorningafter.kellystafford
